    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like <i>charm person</i>, except that mass <i>charm person</i> affects a number of humanoid creatures whose combined Hit Dice don't exceed twice your level. If there are more potential targets than you can affect, you choose them one at a time until you reach the limit of HD you can affect. If you cast mass <i>charm person</i> on only one creature, you ignore the spell's HD limit.</p>"
